					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="Most Content Marketers Are Making These 3 Crushing Mistakes" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20160622194018-GettyImages-57421485.jpeg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
